official_title: Resolution authorizing printing of additional copies of the Senate Hearings on the nomination of Nelson A. Rockefeller to be Vice President of the United States.

summary.text: Authorizes the printing of additional copies of the Senate hearings on the nomination of Nelson A. Rockefeller to be Vice President of the United States for use by the Senate Committee on Rules and Administration.
